id":2342814,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d72228f39d77b1a4f2d593ad05a49d453675267","tid":2342814,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"老鳳有無router推，諗住換好似無得選咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T18:42:12.000Z","msg":"好多電子零件老鳳都唔撚識推咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n砌機轉會可以轉MSI先"},{"pid":"46099d7bf032eed1efafddfe88a99d720943f63e","tid":2342814,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T22:42:09.000Z","msg":"佢依家就係想潛水潛到ces<br />\n點會出水炒番熱單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec0976bfdac22e016e4678c3c18330dfdfc7cc2","tid":2342814,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"debd332bffb5fdf0479875a9656d4080c776123e","tid":2342814,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6ec0976bfdac22e016e4678c3c18330dfdfc7cc2","tid":2342814,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T01:01:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">沙皮狗真係唔吠唔安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n無恥沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)肯向香港手足道歉未?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252543</a><br />\n<br />\n最近沙皮狗經常違反板規證據:<br />\n沙皮狗請回應 有冇報章轉載權； 請LIHKG嚴肅跟進#133680侵犯版權問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194433</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」牠不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c18733ef5db73b4ee9cd942213c66c3c93c7b955","tid":2342814,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9db3fc05c3b146fcaf151b2fa2feee3026feedf9","tid":2342814,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eea05b9e0b95412ece5045daddbe4101bb86a6cc","tid":2342814,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"